desc: We are an online store specializing in lead-free fishing tackle! Our inventory includes ned-rig/midwest finesse style jig heads with multiple hook sizes, colors, and weights available. We even have skirted jigs, weedless (weed guard), swim jigs, and more to come! We have ample stock and take custom orders!

layout.text: We have one of the largest varieties of finesse jigs! Check out our weedless styles, sickle options, skirted jigs, and numerous hook size choices!
